{"tid":1242222,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"見到3毛Post大家唔回應就係最好既回應","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T07:35:41.000Z","uid":15850,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"df7241a3b977af0e3ac99ca322c634adbdb6f49a","tid":1242222,"uid":15850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:33:15.000Z","msg":"你一沉唔住氣回post就等於幫佢地宣傳。結果有關行動或者集會既post就沉曬。<br />\n大家要諗過度過先啊好嗎？"},{"pid":"2870228c7d0193d18173ec46f8b15e230c2ae504","tid":1242222,"uid":15850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:34:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad016b6bc5fbd58164faaf9ee425433461006362","tid":1242222,"uid":15850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3790cb6543c641075fc63bf86403cb0bec4ecd3e","tid":1242222,"uid":257422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b07ecd5e6549bf21e1b810ee284d66d91b9d577","tid":1242222,"uid":15850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:37:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdf0e4d301346158c2464c40e9be6b97a314a873","tid":1242222,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:40:28.000Z","msg":"「黑色五毛警告」分化/五毛/玩膠 User 集中貼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242210</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係需要開個post整合佢地<br />\n<br />\n有時候佢地收得好埋 專登係某啲大post彈出黎<br />\n撩交嗌"},{"pid":"e8c829ebe09d856bae568679cd627e05e3c19ec0","tid":1242222,"uid":15850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdf0e4d301346158c2464c40e9be6b97a314a873","tid":1242222,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:40:28.000Z","msg":"「黑色五毛警告」分化/五毛/玩膠 User 集中貼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242210</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係需要開個post整合佢地<br />\n<br />\n有時候佢地收得好埋 專登係某啲大post彈出黎<br />\n撩交嗌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:52:25.000Z","msg":"同意，唔係個個人都有時間慢慢分析，希望各位可以係最快既時間攞到有效既資訊"},{"pid":"abd40011935c098919d923bde7aef5f